## Usage
```python
from imageio import imread
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
img = imread(root+'/bus.jpg')
normimg = global_norm(img)
rst = matting(normimg)
plt.subplot(121).imshow(img)
plt.subplot(122).imshow(1-rst)
plt.show()
```
